{
  "stem": "19518.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was the most lux-- first of all, it was the most luxurious feeling to be able to go into a shower, and wash yourself, and use that water to your heart's desire.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "After all those months where you were watched, where you weren't allowed to spend an extra minute with a little bit of water that was given to you, you were not allowed.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But this was the most luxurious feeling to have that shower, to get washed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Even it was cold water, but it was water, and then to lie down on a clean sheet on a bed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we were-- we shared the room, about two, four, about six girls shared one room.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we had our private toilet like a sink and a toilet.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The showers were outside in the hallway.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But this was the most luxurious living after all those years that we had to undergo whatever deprivation we went through.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Now, the gypsy men-- there was a roundup, whoever was able to run out into the forest and grab the Nazis and whoever, and they brought them back to camp.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And a few of the gypsy men tried to do to them what they were doing to the-- to not only the Jewish people, but to any Haftling, anybody who was incarcerated, the routine.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the American commandant did not like it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He stopped it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He stopped it, because he felt it's inhuman.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "That the treatment that we were given was inhuman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But we do not have to lose our humanity.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Maybe he was right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I'm not going to be a judge of that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I can't-- I couldn't judge then, and I'm not going to judge now.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Because, first of all, it's too late.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
